high_descs: Turn right and go to the flush toilet
Pick up the toilet paper roll from the stand
Turn around and face the sink cabinet
Open the sink cabinet, put the paper roll inside it
Go to the bathtub to the faucet side
Pick up the empty roll from the side of the bathtub
Go back to the sink cabinet
Open the same drawer and place the empty roll next to the paper roll inside the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Place a toilet paper roll and an empty roll inside the sink cabinet

high_descs: Walk to the toilet paper holder to the left of the toilet.
Pick up the roll of toilet paper.
Face the cabinet below the sink on the right side.
Open the cabinet door on the left, place the toilet paper roll inside the cabinet, and close the door.
Move to face the left side of the tub.
Pick up the empty roll from the edge of the tub.
Move back over to face the cabinet below the sink.
Open the cabinet door on the left, put the empty roll to the left of the full roll in the cabinet, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To move a full roll and an empty roll of toilet paper to the cabinet.
